text: Bought a motorised ceiling mount laundry rack from them 5 years ago at a trade show. The steel cable from the motor snapped last week. I called them up and they provided me a quote for repair. The technician came last Fri to collect the system, and its repaired and installed today. I must say the product is very good quality lasting so many years of daily use. The repair cost is reasonable, turnaround time is also not too bad.
Didn't bother to provide support after sales
